=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Overviews_Operators_ex35 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark pure_tone sound, with fm_or_inharmonic oscillator character around 531 Hz, featuring instant attack and dynamic envelope, with dynamic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: instant
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: dynamic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 530.8607
  harmonic_decay_rate: -2.9824
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0278
  pitch_clarity: 30.9940
  inharmonicity: 0.2104
  type: fm_or_inharmonic
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -4.0418
  resonance_freq: 1593.4570

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Operators Example 35
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Overviews/Operators.html
// Tags: Operators, Overviews
// ---
// --- Example 35 ---
{ (FSinOsc.ar(800) sumsqr: FSinOsc.ar(XLine.kr(200,500,5))) * 0.125 }.play;
